'''Scorpia''' is a large female [[scorpion]] that resides in a cave beneath the [[Scorpion Pit]] located in Wilderness level 53-55. She is the only monster to drop the [[odium shard 3]] and [[malediction shard 3]], which are used to forge the [[odium ward]] and [[malediction ward]], respectively.

